      "span_text": "The sample size was calculated by Cohen sampling method with the possibility of type 1 error calculated at 95% and of type 2 error calculated at 80% the quantitative variability of the control or the study group estimated in 2.63; this is the minimum value between the differences we want to detect, in accordance with the results of El-Sharkawi et al.  ; this difference was estimated at 3.59 on FLACC score, between basal measure and the application of local anesthesia by infiltration."
